</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The cloud hanging over Ladbroke got a little smaller yesterday. There were
no nasty surprises in its annual report and the company has edged in the
direction of further disclosure. It is a welcome trend which would be
assisted by the appointment of some strong, non-executive directors and good
news on slimming of the property portfolio.
