FT  14 MAY 93 / UK Company News: Shaftesbury back into the black
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
SHAFTESBURY, the property group, returned to profits in the six months to
March 31 with Pounds 344,000 pre-tax, against Pounds 1.27m losses. Mr Peter
