30 had been restated to take account of a Pounds 616,000 increase in
provisions against the cost of development properties, leaving the figure at
Pounds 5.3m.
Net revenue from properties was Pounds 2.7m (Pounds 2.53m) plus surplus on
disposals of Pounds 79,000 (Pounds 403,000 deficit) and other operating
income of Pounds 272,000 (Pounds 46,000).
