FT  14 MAY 93 / Pit to close
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
MINERS at Sharlston Colliery, near Wakefield, West Yorkshire, yesterday
agreed to a closure plan as British Coal confirmed it will return to the
High Court next week to seek backing for the closure of other pits.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
